  "text": "The comparison made in this stage includes cross-validation techniques such as Hold-Out (HOCV) and K-fold (KFCV), the introduction of Additive White Gaussian Noise (AWGN) and the combined technique of noise and K-fold validation (KFCV + AWGN). A detailed explanation of these alternatives and an example of their use in a domain with limited information can be found in [CITATION_1] .",
